node.text:
Your health is in your hands, literally 🤍

@apple X Anshuka 🖤

Started this week with a wonderful Yoga & mindfulness session for Apple exploring the Apple Watch series 8 at @sohohousemumbai.

This Series 8 watch by @apple holds the future of health and will revolutionise the way we workout and I loved learning and sharing with each and everyone. 

Thank you to the gorgeous, powerful ladies who came to breathe and flow with me! 

#Yoga #YogaLove #YogaAddict #YogaTeacher #AnshukaYogaWellness #YogaMumbai #ApplexAnshuka #AnshukaParwani #AnshukaYoga
